<div class="application-header">
  <h1 class="application-title">Start New Application</h1>
  <p class="application-subtitle">Apply for an Equity Preservation Mortgage® and access your home's equity while keeping your property</p>
</div>

<div class="dashboard-sections">
  <!-- Start New Application -->
  <div class="summary-section">
    <div class="new-application-card">
      <div class="new-app-content">
        <h4>Ready to apply for an Equity Preservation Mortgage®?</h4>
        <p>Our application process is designed to be simple and straightforward. You can save your progress and return at any time.</p>
        <ul class="benefits-list">
          <li>✓ Access equity while keeping your home</li>
          <li>✓ Flexible loan terms from 10-30 years</li>
          <li>✓ Competitive interest rates</li>
          <li>✓ No monthly mortgage payments required</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="new-app-actions">
        <%= link_to "Start Application", new_dashboard_application_path, class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- How It Works -->
  <div class="summary-section">
    <h3 class="summary-section-title">How It Works</h3>
    <div class="how-it-works-grid">
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-number">1</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h4>Property Details</h4>
          <p>Tell us about your property including its address, value, and ownership details.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-number">2</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h4>Loan Configuration</h4>
          <p>Choose your loan terms, mortgage type, and income payout preferences.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-number">3</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h4>Review & Submit</h4>
          <p>Review your application summary and submit for processing.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-number">4</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h4>Approval Process</h4>
          <p>We'll arrange property valuation and review your application for final approval.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Eligibility Requirements -->
  <div class="summary-section">
    <h3 class="summary-section-title">Eligibility Requirements</h3>
    <div class="eligibility-grid">
      <div class="eligibility-item">
        <div class="eligibility-icon">🏠</div>
        <div class="eligibility-content">
          <h5>Property Ownership</h5>
          <p>You must own your property outright or have significant equity available.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="eligibility-item">
        <div class="eligibility-icon">📊</div>
        <div class="eligibility-content">
          <h5>Property Value</h5>
          <p>Minimum property value requirements apply. We'll arrange an independent valuation.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="eligibility-item">
        <div class="eligibility-icon">👥</div>
        <div class="eligibility-content">
          <h5>Age Requirements</h5>
          <p>Applicants must meet minimum age requirements for eligibility.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="eligibility-item">
        <div class="eligibility-icon">📄</div>
        <div class="eligibility-content">
          <h5>Documentation</h5>
          <p>Valid identification and property documentation will be required.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <div class="summary-section">
    <h3 class="summary-section-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h3>
    <div class="faq-list">
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h5>What is an Equity Preservation Mortgage®?</h5>
        <p>An Equity Preservation Mortgage® allows you to access the equity in your home while maintaining ownership. You receive regular income payments while preserving your property for the future.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h5>Do I need to make monthly payments?</h5>
        <p>No monthly payments are required. The loan is typically repaid when the property is sold or at the end of the loan term, depending on your chosen mortgage type.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h5>How long does the application process take?</h5>
        <p>The application process typically takes 2-4 weeks, including property valuation and document review. We'll keep you informed every step of the way.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h5>Can I pay off the loan early?</h5>
        <p>Yes, you can pay off your loan early. Contact our team to discuss early repayment options and any applicable fees.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<% content_for :help_section do %>
  <%= render 'shared/account_help' %>
<% end %>